headline.print_headline: Boeing to Feel Little Impact From Train Derailment-Analysts
headline.main: Boeing to Feel Little Impact From Train Derailment-Analysts

lead_paragraph: Boeing Co will easily recover financially from a 19-car train derailment in Montana last week that sent three fuselages for its popular 737 jetliner tumbling down a steep embankment toward a river and damaged other plane parts, analysts said on Sunday.
